REQUIRED ATTRIBUTION FORMAT

When using DDC CWICR data in any project, product, publication,
application, or derivative work, you MUST include the following
attribution:

    "DDC CWICR by Artem Boiko / DataDrivenConstruction"
    https://github.com/datadrivenconstruction/OpenConstructionEstimate-DDC-CWICR

Examples of appropriate attribution:

  * In a README or documentation:
      Data source: DDC CWICR by Artem Boiko / DataDrivenConstruction
      https://github.com/datadrivenconstruction/OpenConstructionEstimate-DDC-CWICR
      Licensed under CC BY 4.0

  * In a web application footer or "About" page:
      Construction cost data provided by DDC CWICR
      © Artem Boiko / DataDrivenConstruction — CC BY 4.0

  * In an academic paper or report:
      Boiko, A. (2025). DDC CWICR — Construction Work Items, Costs &
      Resources. DataDrivenConstruction.
      https://github.com/datadrivenconstruction/OpenConstructionEstimate-DDC-CWICR

  * In a mobile or desktop application:
      "About" or "Credits" screen must include:
      Cost data: DDC CWICR by DataDrivenConstruction (CC BY 4.0)

If you modified the data, you must also indicate what changes were made.

